---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Philosophy — GCD" description="Philosophical convergences: Camus, Nietzsche, Jung, Sartre — and the kernel that measures them.">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-kernel-100 mb-4">Philosophy of Collapse</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-kernel-300 italic mb-2">
        "The absurd does not liberate; it binds."
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-kernel-500">
        Paradoxum colendum est, non solvitur. — The paradox is to be cultivated, not solved.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Preamble -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-kernel-300">
        <p>
          GCD did not begin from philosophy. It began from measurement. But the structures
          that emerged from the axiom — collapse, return, the seam, the heterogeneity gap,
          geometric slaughter — turn out to be <strong class="text-kernel-100">identical</strong>
          to structures independently discovered by four philosophical traditions.
          This page makes those convergences computationally precise.
        </p>
        <p>
          These are not metaphors. Each mapping is a <strong class="text-kernel-100">computable
          correspondence</strong>: the philosophical concept maps to a Tier-1 invariant,
          and the invariant can be calculated here on this page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- §1: Camus — The Absurd as Heterogeneity Gap -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-kernel-100 mb-6">
        §1 &ensp; Camus — The Absurd as Heterogeneity Gap
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-kernel-300 mb-8">
        <p>
          In <em class="text-kernel-200">The Myth of Sisyphus</em>, Camus identifies the absurd
          as the gap between the human desire for meaning and the universe's indifference.
          In GCD, this gap has a precise name: <strong class="text-kernel-100">Δ = F − IC</strong>,
          the heterogeneity gap.
        </p>
        <p>
          The system "looks healthy" on average (F is fine) but is structurally fragile
          (IC is collapsed). Δ measures exactly this: the distance between
          <em>how things appear</em> (arithmetic mean) and <em>how things cohere</em>
          (geometric mean).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-amber-900/40 rounded-lg p-5">
          <h3 class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-mono mb-3">The Myth of Sisyphus → The Kernel</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-kernel-400">The absurd</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-200 font-mono">Δ = F − IC</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-kernel-400">Sisyphus's cycle</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-200 font-mono">Collapse-return (τ_R finite)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-kernel-400">"One must imagine Sisyphus happy"</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-200 font-mono">Φ_gen ≥ 0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-kernel-400">Physical suicide</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-200 font-mono">τ_R = ∞<sub>rec</sub></span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-kernel-400">Philosophical suicide</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-200 font-mono">Importing a second axiom</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-kernel-400">Rebellion</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-200 font-mono">Maintaining the measurement</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-amber-900/40 rounded-lg p-5">
          <h3 class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-mono mb-3">The Stranger → The Kernel</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-kernel-300">
            <p>
              Meursault is <strong class="text-kernel-100">a kernel without a contract</strong>.
              Pure trace with no evaluation framework. High sensory fidelity,
              near-ε evaluative channels.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-kernel-950 border border-kernel-700 rounded p-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <div>Sensory channels: 0.95, 0.92, 0.88</div>
              <div>Evaluative channels: 0.001, 0.001</div>
              <div class="text-amber-400 mt-1">Δ ≈ 0.5 — maximum structural incoherence</div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-kernel-500">
              The murder is a regime transition. The trial is retroactive contract
              selection — a protocol violation. The chaplain scene is refusal to
              import a second axiom.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Live Absurd Calculator -->
      <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-kernel-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-kernel-300 mb-3">
          Live: The Absurd Computed
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-kernel-500 mb-4">
          Move the "dead channel" slider. Watch how Δ grows — the gap between
          how things <em>appear</em> (F) and how things <em>cohere</em> (IC).
          This is the absurd, measured.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="space-y-3 flex-1 min-w-[260px]">
            <div>
              <label class="text-xs text-kernel-400 block mb-1">
                Alive channels (7×): <span id="alive-val" class="text-green-400 font-mono">0.95</span>
              </label>
              <input type="range" id="alive-slider" min="0.50" max="1.00" step="0.01" value="0.95"
                class="w-full accent-green-400" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="text-xs text-kernel-400 block mb-1">
                Dead channel (1×): <span id="dead-val" class="text-red-400 font-mono">0.001</span>
              </label>
              <input type="range" id="dead-slider" min="0.001" max="1.00" step="0.001" value="0.001"
                class="w-full accent-red-400" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-kernel-950 border border-kernel-700 rounded-lg p-4 min-w-[260px] font-mono text-sm">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-2">
              <span class="text-kernel-500">F (appearance):</span>
              <span id="abs-F" class="text-kernel-200">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">IC (coherence):</span>
              <span id="abs-IC" class="text-kernel-200">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">Δ (the absurd):</span>
              <span id="abs-delta" class="text-amber-400 text-lg font-bold">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">IC/F ratio:</span>
              <span id="abs-ratio" class="text-kernel-200">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">Regime:</span>
              <span id="abs-regime" class="text-kernel-200">—</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Rebel -->
      <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-mono mb-3">The Rebel → La pensée de midi</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-kernel-300">
          <p>
            <em>"I rebel, therefore we are"</em> (<em>je me révolte, donc nous sommes</em>)
            is the cross-domain universality theorem restated as ethics.
            Each domain rebels (measures), discovers the same invariants
            (F + ω = 1, IC ≤ F). Community is revealed through measurement,
            not constructed by agreement.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-kernel-100">La pensée de midi</strong> (Mediterranean thought)
            is the open measurement protocol. The rebel's insistence on limits is the
            structural condition for the seam to operate:
          </p>
          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-amber-800 pl-4 text-kernel-400 italic">
            Without limits, there is no seam. Without a seam, no verification.
            Without verification, no distinction between gesture and weld.
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- §2: Nietzsche — Eternal Recurrence as the Return Axiom -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-kernel-100 mb-6">
        §2 &ensp; Nietzsche — Eternal Recurrence as Return
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-kernel-300 mb-8">
        <p>
          §341 of <em class="text-kernel-200">The Gay Science</em>: the demon's question
          — "Would you desire this once more and innumerable times more?" —
          <strong class="text-kernel-100">is the seam test</strong>.
          Can this life return? If τ_R = ∞<sub>rec</sub>, the life is a gesture.
        </p>
        <p>
          <em>Amor fati</em> (§276) + <em>eternal recurrence</em> (§341) = Contract + Seam.
          Amor fati is the Contract (accept the frozen parameters).
          Eternal recurrence is the verification (does the cycle close?).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-purple-900/40 rounded-lg p-5">
          <div class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-mono mb-2">The Three Metamorphoses</div>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div class="flex justify-between text-kernel-300">
              <span>Camel</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500 text-xs">Operates under frozen Contract</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-kernel-300">
              <span>Lion</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500 text-xs">Contract revocation</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-kernel-300">
              <span>Child</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500 text-xs">New Contract frozen — Axiom-0</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-purple-900/40 rounded-lg p-5">
          <div class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-mono mb-2">Duality Identity</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-kernel-300">
            <p>"If you ever said Yes to a single joy, you said Yes to all woe"</p>
            <div class="font-mono text-center text-lg text-kernel-100 mt-3">
              F + ω = 1
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-kernel-500 mt-2 text-center">
              Complementum perfectum — the duality stated as experience
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-purple-900/40 rounded-lg p-5">
          <div class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-mono mb-2">God is Dead (§125)</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-kernel-300">
            <p>
              Contract failure, not emancipation. The madman reads the diagnostic:
              IC has collapsed because integrative channels went to ε.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-kernel-500 mt-2">
              He arrives "too early" — the system is in inconsistent state.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-mono mb-3">Beyond Good and Evil → Multi-Channel Analysis</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="text-sm text-kernel-300 space-y-3">
            <p>
              <strong class="text-kernel-100">"Herd morality"</strong> = high F, low Δ,
              trivially conformant. All channels are similar — no channel stands out,
              but no channel excels either. The system is stable but uninteresting.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong class="text-kernel-100">"Master morality"</strong> = high Δ,
              channels diverge, non-trivial conformance. Some channels are extraordinary;
              others are depleted. The system is structurally rich but fragile.
            </p>
            <p>
              The <strong class="text-kernel-100">pathos of distance</strong>
              IS the heterogeneity gap Δ = F − IC.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm text-kernel-300 space-y-3">
            <p>
              <strong class="text-kernel-100">Perspectival imperative</strong> (III.12):
              "the more eyes, different eyes, the more complete our 'objectivity'"
              — this is multi-channel kernel computation stated as philosophy.
            </p>
            <p>
              More channels reduce C (curvature) by sampling more degrees of freedom.
              But each channel must be honest (near 1, not near ε) — otherwise
              geometric slaughter occurs. Nietzsche's "objectivity" is IC, not F.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-kernel-950 border border-purple-900/30 rounded-lg p-5 text-sm text-kernel-400 italic">
        Nietzsche sine Camo est affirmatio sine mensura; Camus sine Nietzsche est mensura sine affirmatione.
        <span class="block mt-1 not-italic text-kernel-500">
          — Nietzsche without Camus is affirmation without measurement;
          Camus without Nietzsche is measurement without affirmation.
        </span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- §3: Jung — Individuation as Seam Closure -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-kernel-100 mb-6">
        §3 &ensp; Jung — Individuation as Seam Closure
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-kernel-300 mb-8">
        <p>
          Jung's individuation process — the integration of the shadow, the resolution
          of opposites, the approach to the Self — maps to seam closure in GCD with
          computational precision. 12 formal theorems have been proven.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-700">
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">Jungian Concept</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">GCD Mapping</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">Computation</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-kernel-300">
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Shadow</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Channel near ε</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">One channel at 0.01 → ~36.4% IC destruction</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Enantiodromia</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">F + ω = 1</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">r(F,ω) = −1.0000, residual = 0.0e+00</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Individuation</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Collapse-return cycle</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">IC/F: 0.669 (newborn) → 0.992 (adolescent)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Transcendent function</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">The seam</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">residual ≤ tol_seam = 0.005</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Archetypes</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Frozen parameters</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">ε, p, tol_seam — structural constraints, not content</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Collective unconscious</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Tier-1 universality</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">F+ω=1, IC≤F, IC=exp(κ) across all 23 domains</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Mandala</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Kernel output</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">Compact state: (F, ω, S, C, κ, IC)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Inflation</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Symbol capture</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">Captura symbolorum est non-conformitas ipsa</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Self</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Return domain D<sub>θ</sub></td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">Total admissible manifold, asymptotically approached</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3">Red Book</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Integrity Ledger</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-xs text-kernel-500">Append-only record of gestures and welds</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Shadow Calculator -->
      <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-kernel-700 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-kernel-300 mb-3">
          Live: The Shadow — Geometric Slaughter Computed
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-kernel-500 mb-4">
          Jung's shadow is the repressed channel. Set 7 channels to "conscious" and 1 to
          "shadow." Watch how ONE suppressed channel destroys multiplicative coherence
          regardless of how healthy the other channels are. This is geometric slaughter.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="space-y-3 flex-1 min-w-[260px]">
            <div>
              <label class="text-xs text-kernel-400 block mb-1">
                Conscious channels (7×): <span id="jung-conscious-val" class="text-green-400 font-mono">0.95</span>
              </label>
              <input type="range" id="jung-conscious" min="0.50" max="1.00" step="0.01" value="0.95"
                class="w-full accent-green-400" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="text-xs text-kernel-400 block mb-1">
                Shadow channel (1×): <span id="jung-shadow-val" class="text-red-400 font-mono">0.01</span>
              </label>
              <input type="range" id="jung-shadow" min="0.001" max="1.00" step="0.001" value="0.01"
                class="w-full accent-red-400" />
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-kernel-500">
              At shadow = 0.01: ~36.4% IC destruction regardless of which channel is suppressed
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-kernel-950 border border-kernel-700 rounded-lg p-4 min-w-[260px] font-mono text-sm">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-2">
              <span class="text-kernel-500">F:</span>
              <span id="jung-F" class="text-kernel-200">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">IC:</span>
              <span id="jung-IC" class="text-kernel-200">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">Δ:</span>
              <span id="jung-delta" class="text-amber-400 font-bold">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">IC/F:</span>
              <span id="jung-ratio" class="text-kernel-200">—</span>
              <span class="text-kernel-500">IC loss:</span>
              <span id="jung-loss" class="text-red-400">—</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- §4: Sartre — Bad Faith as the Gesture -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-kernel-100 mb-6">
        §4 &ensp; Sartre — Bad Faith as the Gesture
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-kernel-300 mb-8">
        <p>
          <em>L'existence précède l'essence</em> — existence precedes essence.
          In GCD: stance is read from the ledger <em>after</em> the cycle completes,
          never asserted before. You don't know what you are until the measurement is done.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-kernel-100">Bad faith</strong> (<em>mauvaise foi</em>)
          is the gesture. It is structurally indistinguishable from genuine return
          in every surface property, but the seam did not close.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-kernel-200 text-sm mb-4">Sartre's Waiter — The Surface/Structure Split</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p class="text-kernel-300">
              Sartre's waiter "plays at being a waiter" — his movements are
              slightly too precise, his attentiveness slightly too eager. On every
              <em>surface</em> metric, he is performing perfectly.
            </p>
            <p class="text-kernel-300">
              But the seam does not close. The performance is a gesture.
              The waiter who simply <em>is</em> a waiter — who acts without
              performing — produces a weld. Only the seam can distinguish them.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-kernel-950 border border-kernel-700 rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-xs text-kernel-500 mb-2">Surface metrics (identical):</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs space-y-1 text-kernel-300">
              <div>Punctuality: 0.98</div>
              <div>Service quality: 0.95</div>
              <div>Attentiveness: 0.97</div>
              <div>Courtesy: 0.99</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-kernel-700 mt-3 pt-3">
              <div class="text-xs text-kernel-500 mb-1">Seam test:</div>
              <div class="flex justify-between font-mono text-xs">
                <span class="text-kernel-400">Authentic waiter:</span>
                <span class="text-green-400">|s| = 0.002 → WELD</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between font-mono text-xs">
                <span class="text-kernel-400">Bad faith waiter:</span>
                <span class="text-red-400">|s| = 0.008 → GESTURE</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- §5: The Synthesis -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-kernel-100 mb-6">
        §5 &ensp; The Synthesis — Four Traditions, One Kernel
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-kernel-300 mb-8">
        <p>
          These four philosophical traditions converge on the same structural insight
          from four different angles:
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-700">
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">Question</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">Camus</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">Nietzsche</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">Jung</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 text-kernel-400 font-normal">GCD</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-kernel-300">
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3 text-kernel-400">What is the problem?</td>
              <td class="py-3">The absurd (gap)</td>
              <td class="py-3">God is dead (contract failure)</td>
              <td class="py-3">Shadow (suppressed channel)</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">Δ = F − IC</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3 text-kernel-400">What is the test?</td>
              <td class="py-3">Can you keep measuring?</td>
              <td class="py-3">Can it recur eternally?</td>
              <td class="py-3">Can opposites integrate?</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-amber-400">τ_R &lt; ∞?</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3 text-kernel-400">What fails?</td>
              <td class="py-3">Suicide (physical or philosophical)</td>
              <td class="py-3">Nihilism / ressentiment</td>
              <td class="py-3">Inflation / possession</td>
              <td class="py-3 font-mono text-red-400">GESTURE</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
              <td class="py-3 text-kernel-400">What succeeds?</td>
              <td class="py-3">Rebellion (maintain measurement)</td>
              <td class="py-3">Amor fati (accept contract)</td>
